{"tid":525458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣漁民捕獲「外星怪魚」　全球僅3處有","createTime":"2018-01-10T16:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T21:28:59.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed13739b2fa177c0ec1e137c388bb8540238ed2","tid":525458,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180110/1275859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180110%2F1275859%2F&d=j2F5cu9y%2FnzfRW17Xc3QejM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=9f71cecf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180110%2F1275859%2F&h=e62b9756\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180110/1275859/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n台灣水試所東部海洋研究中心去年12月，在東河鄉外海捕獲5尾外型貌似電影「異形」的怪魚，英國《太陽報》、《每日郵報》以及日本等各國媒體還引述報導，而根據資料顯示，這種魚其實真正名稱為「卡氏尖頷烏鯊」，全世界僅有三處地方出現過，但載著專家出海的老漁民一派輕鬆的說：「其實我每星期都會捕到這種怪魚，因為沒經濟價值，就都放回海中」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_c5d518fabfab528408557ef6620db875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180110%2F640_c5d518fabfab528408557ef6620db875.jpg&h=9640d13b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n5條罕見烏鯊被捕獲後，其中1條倖存，但放入缸中卻疑因肝臟受損底部朝天，最後仍難逃一死，只是這個研究計劃最後卻未有人接手繼續研究。根據紀錄，1986年卡氏尖頷烏鯊在日本愛知縣330公尺深海處首次被人捕獲，第2尾是在1987年於德島縣捕獲，目前僅有日本、夏威夷和台灣有捕獲紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_05ea47d147aae829e846e079be6e03c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180110%2F640_05ea47d147aae829e846e079be6e03c9.jpg&h=50073cbf&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3085751d96897adaf987bbcad19319783e37dcc5","tid":525458,"uid":93640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_c5d518fabfab528408557ef6620db875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180110%2F640_c5d518fabfab528408557ef6620db875.jpg&h=9640d13b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">很想要吧</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d213ff36dcc63c42996c37bb0cd89c2d17c534e1","tid":525458,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"異形咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558e320d5746d8c1dd90af21e3c483a4276899a3","tid":525458,"uid":139815,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"台灣連啲魚都咸濕淫賤過人"},{"pid":"de801a3ce7726924afdc3d18fbdf34f3670c402c","tid":525458,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">日本媒體也報導台灣捕獲5條罕見「卡氏尖頷烏鯊」一事。（圖擷自日本《sputniknews》）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php62bhZp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php62bhZp.jpg&h=613e2121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南媒體也報導台灣捕獲5條罕見「卡氏尖頷烏鯊」一事。（圖擷自越南《VN Express》）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpRCeSCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpRCeSCA.jpg&h=e0b797f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水產試驗所表示，這種屬於烏鯊科 （Etmopteridae）的卡氏尖頷烏鯊，有著好比鯊魚的尖牙，與毒蛇的毒牙，因此英文俗名才稱牠為「毒蛇鯊魚」；這種魚白天主要棲息在300至400公尺的深海處，晚上則會在水深150公尺處活動，目前全世界僅於台灣、日本、夏威夷發現本種。<br />\n<br />\n英國網友看到卡氏尖頷烏鯊的報導後，驚呼「我到底是看到了什麼魚！」、「這魚看起來就很恐怖，應該不要隨便靠近」，也有網友覺得這種魚有著漂亮的「藍眼」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2307499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2307499&d=j2F5cu9y%2FnzfRW17Xc3QejM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=83a47b60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2307499&h=9d2d5fc7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2307499</a></div>"},{"pid":"fa69afb8ba81ad50d54b16cb5e787107e3857322","tid":525458,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"558e320d5746d8c1dd90af21e3c483a4276899a3","tid":525458,"uid":139815,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"台灣連啲魚都咸濕淫賤過人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"根據紀錄，1986年卡氏尖頷烏鯊在日本愛知縣330公尺深海處首次被人捕獲，第2條是在1987年於德島縣捕獲，目前僅有日本、夏威夷和台灣有捕獲紀錄。"},{"pid":"72c08b0185bfab5409fd03ded0d85a9349fe1ac7","tid":525458,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"深海條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好鬼高質啊 快d過嚟上面搵我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84117d7ccd95dd95245ea86531a21f8b64191066","tid":525458,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"飛機杯"},{"pid":"85a8ecb5215802c94049eeb3ece81f38498dc9ea","tid":525458,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"Venom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee35cb71a8a58b8e58f09bd7002ec9f5ed6802b","tid":525458,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84117d7ccd95dd95245ea86531a21f8b64191066","tid":525458,"uid":4525,"li